1c2620624226150a7780b5422a","tid":1717982,"uid":47110,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:40:56.000Z","msg":"上訴幾時有結果<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ed1adac0524930e3b61850a0e1d2fb5aebb6c4ee","tid":1717982,"uid":315251,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T17:46:04.000Z","msg":"美國《時代》雜誌公布「100 NEXT」名單，選出全球正在改變未來的100位新星。入選的包括本土民主前線的前發言人梁天琦，報道形容他雖然身在獄中，但仍然是不少香港抗爭者的精神領袖。<br />\n<br />\n《時代》雜誌形容，梁天琦因為參與2016年旺角騷亂而入獄，但對於近月高呼「光復香港，時代革命」的示威者而言，他仍然是一位精神領袖。他將本土主義帶入香港主流，有關他的紀錄片《地厚天高》亦被視為抗爭者必看的作品。<br />\n<br />\n《時代》雜誌指，雖然在囚的梁天琦未能參與連月的反送中運動，但他在今年7月仍然向香港人發公開信。他在信中懇請大家不要被仇恨支配自己，在危難中，不要以自己寶貴的生命與當權者對賭，要時刻保持警覺與思考。<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GejvnRs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGejvnRs.png&h=7a2c5f23&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://thestandnews.com/politics/梁天琦入選時代雜誌-100-next-名單-被視為香港抗爭者精神領袖/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%A2%81%E5%A4%A9%E7%90%A6%E5%85%A5%E9%81%B8%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E9%9B%9C%E8%AA%8C-100-next-%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE-%E8%A2%AB%E8%A6%96%E7%82%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E8%80%85%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E9%A0%98%E8%A2%96%2F&d=jGmFyvXa%2BxCeqK61Wy4eywwUaSA5OUQt3qQG7WIDhAk%3D&h=79ec7bdd\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%E6%A2%81%E5%A4%A9%E7%90%A6%E5%85%A5%E9%81%B8%E6%99%82%E4%BB%A3%E9%9B%9C%E8%AA%8C-100-next-%E5%90%8D%E5%96%AE-%E8%A2%AB%E8%A6%96%E7%82%BA%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E6%8A%97%E7%88%AD%E8%80%85%E7%B2%BE%E7%A5%9E%E9%A0%98%E8%A2%96%2F&h=7bb86fb1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://thestandnews.com/politics/梁天琦入選時代雜誌-100-next-名單-被視為香港抗爭者精神領袖/</a>"},{"pid":"539e26b4d42eb65b61f0dbfb192bc96db885f941","tid":1717982,"uid":84657,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-13T18:23:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ee952b4ee0c9d2f03ff075b4b2ec3df5f753e95b","tid":1717982,"uid":7